text:
anyone knows how to set redirect url after submitting reset your password form ?

`/_hcms/mem/reset/request?redirect_url=/&amp;reset_success=true&amp;user_email=<mailto:test@test.com|test@test.com>`

(im using login required pages and set up my custom login/register/reset password templates (see first image) ) (edited)
image.png
```{% module "membership_rich_text" path="<@UDA553DRD>/rich_text" label="Rich Text" html="&lt;div class='login-h1'&gt;&lt;h1&gt;&lt;b&gt;Reset Password&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" %}
         {% password_reset_request "password_reset_request"
          submit_button_text= "Send Reset Email",
          redirect_url="<https://google.com>"
          %}
           &lt;div&gt;
          {% module_block module 'membership_admin_content'
            label='Contact admin',
            path='<@UDA553DRD>/rich_text'
          %}
            {% module_attribute 'html' %}
               &lt;p class="register-p-50"&gt;
                Not registered yet?
               &lt;/p&gt;
               &lt;div class="actions"&gt;
                 &lt;a class="hs-button primary large" href="/loan-referral-platform-registration"&gt;Register&lt;/a&gt;
               &lt;/div&gt;
                  &lt;p class="register-p-50"&gt;
                  Having trouble? &lt;a href="{{'mailto:' ~ site_settings.membershipWebsiteAdmin}}"&gt;Contact us&lt;/a&gt;.
                &lt;/p&gt;
            {% end_module_attribute %}
          {% end_module_block %}
              &lt;/div&gt;


                 &lt;/div&gt;```
